00:00:24.640 --> 00:00:25.520 line:20%
Preesha.

00:00:26.680 --> 00:00:28.800 line:20%
Tolong berikan susu ini
kepada Kakak Ipar Malhar.

00:00:29.880 --> 00:00:30.760 line:20%
Hei, berhenti.

00:00:33.600 --> 00:00:34.920 line:20%
Kembalikan gelasnya, Preesha.

00:00:38.480 --> 00:00:40.200 line:20%
Apa yang kamu lakukan?
Kembali ke sana.

00:00:44.120 --> 00:00:45.240 line:20%
Menantu perempuan Rukmini.

00:00:46.160 --> 00:00:47.560 line:20%
Apakah kakimu terikat

00:00:47.760 --> 00:00:50.080 line:20%
bahwa kamu meminta Preesha
untuk mengantarkan susu?

00:00:50.800 --> 00:00:52.120
Tidak seperti itu, Ibu Mertua.

00:00:52.200 --> 00:00:53.600
Jangan membuat alasan.

00:00:54.680 --> 00:00:56.560
Maksudku, aku mengerti.
Anda pasti berpikir karena kami

00:00:56.640 --> 00:00:59.720
